title: Kathryn ‘Michelle’ Dick | Obituaries | state-journal.com
text:
Kathryn “Michelle” Dick, 42, wife of Alan Michael Dick, passed away Monday, December 25, 2023. Services will be held at Bethel Baptist Church on Wednesday, January 3, 2024, at 11 a.m. with Rev. Josh Rucker officiating. Burial will follow at Bethel Baptist Church Cemetery. Visitation will be held at Bethel Baptist Church from 5 p.m. until 8 p.m. on Tuesday, January 2, 2024.
Kathryn “Michelle” Dick
She was born in Frankfort, Kentucky, on August 18, 1981, to Deborah Hortenbury and John Anglin.
